'''Michael B. Yaffe''' is the Chief Scientific Editor ([[Editor in Chief]]) of the peer reviewed science journal ''[[Science Signaling]]'' published by the [[American Association for the Advancement of Science]]. <ref name=signal>
{{cite web
 | title =Editorial Board
 | work =
 | publisher =Science Signaling (AAAS)
 | date =
 | url = http://stke.sciencemag.org/about/edboard.dtl
 | doi =
 | accessdate =2012-08-27}}</ref>
He is currently a Professor of Biology and Biological Engineering at the [[Massachusetts Institute of Technology]]. He received his Ph.D. in 1987 from the [[Case Western Reserve University]] which is where he also received his M.D. in 1989.  <ref name=koch> 
