==Research==
The main focus of Yaffe's research is decoding natural [[cell signaling]] pathway behavior using [[bioinformatics]], [[combinatorial chemistry]], [[cell biology]], [[biochemistry|physical biochemistry]], [[structural biology]] and [[molecular genetics]]. <ref> 
